{"tid":781812,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"收音機算唔算係蓋清最爆既事？","createTime":"2018-08-16T08:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T05:15:41.000Z","uid":17606,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5319c5ac9ff62c6d25957bd3304a3e9d87ac3aec","tid":781812,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:10:27.000Z","msg":"一名自稱「小皮球」的男子昨主動致電本報，首先聲稱自己只是「玩」和「吹水」，該題目只是抄自其他網站，當日他其實沒有干擾考試。言談間，他要求記者不要再報道，又多次問記者這樣「吹水」是否犯法，也提及過往曾發生多宗網上留言惹官非事件。<br />\n然而，他後來又反口指自己只是「小皮球」朋友，並非事主本人。當記者再致電他時，他說「小皮球」沒有興趣回應。<br />\n「小皮球」昨在網上留言，不斷強調自己只是「吹水」，但不少網友指他「知衰」，有人揶揄說相信他的解釋，「不過你都係留番同法官講啦。」更有網友留言披露他姓高。"},{"pid":"5d2d05d6b557d9072f85a31265af589694d14c89","tid":781812,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:11:44.000Z","msg":"算"},{"pid":"161c0bb548353c85c21403e2715bbb8aa58f0eb0","tid":781812,"uid":29929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:11:51.000Z","msg":"搏出位姐"},{"pid":"00b0c3d151b40264acd5ec75ffdc6f2e8c88b632","tid":781812,"uid":29929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:12:57.000Z","msg":"當記者再致電他時，他說「小皮球」沒有興趣回應。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記者一早起蓋清底<br />\n當年記者快d爆料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c058cc9cc65de9e3c23f90a65dde872c56b8c76","tid":781812,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:15:38.000Z","msg":"蓋清每次睇返篇新聞會唔會有dd感觸"},{"pid":"3401ad117048cfa6988fd0db286ab4d4c878b2b6","tid":781812,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00b0c3d151b40264acd5ec75ffdc6f2e8c88b632","tid":781812,"uid":29929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:12:57.000Z","msg":"當記者再致電他時，他說「小皮球」沒有興趣回應。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo